# Build-context trimming for the repo-root images: Dockerfile.keeper
# (keeper/liquidation bots) and Dockerfile.fullstack (frontend SPA + API).
# backend/ and frontend/ SOURCE must stay in context for the full-stack build;
# only the heavy generated/installed directories below are excluded. The
# backend/ and frontend/ services that build from their own roots have their
# own .dockerignore files.
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
artifacts
cache
typechain
typechain-types
coverage
**/coverage
.openzeppelin
docs-site
docs
landing
sdk
test
.vscode
*.log
*.tsbuildinfo
